data.title: CTIF - International Association of Fire Services for Safer Citizens through Skilled Firefighters
data.meta_description: CTIF was founded in 1900 in Paris as “Comité Technique International de prevention et d'extinction de Feu”, for the purposes of encouraging and promoting co-operation among firefighters and other experts in Fire & Rescue throughout the world.
